{
  "id": "6a02bcd294b7d3ba594e52bb",
  "title": "輪郭",
  "created": 1778564309,
  "updated": 1779456718,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a02bcd294b7d3ba594e52bb",
      "text": "輪郭",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564309,
      "updated": 1778564309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bcbf00000000004555c8",
      "text": " [デライト]（[デルン]）の情報構成単位[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564309,
      "updated": 1778564569
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bcd800000000004555ca",
      "text": "  [Cosense] でいう[ページ]に相当する",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564334,
      "updated": 1778564350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bce800000000004555cb",
      "text": "  英語では普通に outline",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564350,
      "updated": 1778564379
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bd3e00000000004555d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564437,
      "updated": 1778564438
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1059ec000000000044a86a",
      "text": " 輪郭には[知番]というIDが云々[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779456494,
      "updated": 1779456662
    },
    {
      "id": "6a105ab1000000000044a86c",
      "text": " [知名]めっちゃ大事",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779456690,
      "updated": 1779456700
    },
    {
      "id": "6a105abd000000000044a86d",
      "text": "  [デライトの検索]では知名を活用する",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779456702,
      "updated": 1779456718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1059ed000000000044a86b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779456494,
      "updated": 1779456494
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bd1200000000004555cd",
      "text": " Twitter 時代の「[ツイート]」のように、聞けばすぐデライトのそれを連想できる用語にしたかった[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564392,
      "updated": 1778564588
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bcc600000000004555c9",
      "text": "  「輪郭」は日本語の単語としての理解しやすさ・出現頻度がちょうどよかった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564316,
      "updated": 1778564557
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02be5400000000004555d4",
      "text": "   誰でも知っているが日常的に使われることは少ない言葉",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564714,
      "updated": 1778564782
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02c00800000000004555d5",
      "text": "    いっそ再定義してしまおう",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778565150,
      "updated": 1778565160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02c4520000000000b454fd",
      "text": "   しばしば「輪」と略し、1輪、2輪と助数詞としても使う",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778566249,
      "updated": 1778566285
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02c46e0000000000b454fe",
      "text": "    [デジタルガーデン]のイメージで花の助数詞にかけている",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778566276,
      "updated": 1778566337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bdb700000000004555d2",
      "text": "  それ以前は「描」(vio) という用語で呼んでいたことがある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564557,
      "updated": 1778566000
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02be0600000000004555d3",
      "text": "   これだとイメージも掴みにくく日常に溶け込みにくい",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564636,
      "updated": 1778564875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a02bd3900000000004555cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778564432,
      "updated": 1778564432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06924c0000000000d4dcba",
      "text": "デライト用語は基本的にとっつきづらいのだが、なかでも輪郭の違和感は凄かった[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815565,
      "updated": 1778815602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06930b0000000000d4dcbf",
      "text": " [知番]、[知名]、描写はまだわかる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815757,
      "updated": 1779456360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06926d0000000000d4dcbc",
      "text": " 投稿を輪郭と表すなんて聞いたことがない",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815598,
      "updated": 1778815622
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0692d30000000000d4dcbe",
      "text": "  輪郭という呼び名にピンと来ない",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815701,
      "updated": 1778815727
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0692b00000000000d4dcbd",
      "text": " 自分の脳内辞書で「輪郭」がデライトのそれを指すように書き換わったので今はなんとも思わない",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815666,
      "updated": 1778815699
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06924f0000000000d4dcbb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778815569,
      "updated": 1778815569
    }
  ]
}